2003-09-03 01:22:56 GMT	Colin Walters <walters@verbum.org>	patch-16

    Summary:
      merge with mainline
    Revision:
      rhythmbox--cvs--1.0--patch-16

    merge with mainline
    
    Patches applied:
    
     * desrt@desrt.ca--2003/rhythmbox--mainline--1.0--patch-5
       statusbar state wasn't synced at startup and therefore was always initially visible regardless of the gconf setting.  introduced a sync call in rb-shell.c just before the main window is presented
    
     * walters@rhythmbox.org--2003/rhythmbox--mainline--1.0--patch-19
       merge with CVS
    
     * walters@rhythmbox.org--2003/rhythmbox--mainline--1.0--patch-20
