2003-09-02  Yann Rouillard <yann@cvs.gnome.org>
                                                                                       
        * shell/rb-playlist-manager.c: (load_playlist_response_cb):
                                                                                       
        Escaped the playlist filename to load.
                                                                                       
        * shell/rb-playlist-manager.c: (rb_playlist_manager_validate_name),
        (rb_playlist_manager_new_playlist_dialog),
        (rb_playlist_manager_rename_playlist_dialog):
                                                                                       
        Tiny ui improvements: new playlist dialog now always
        displays an unused playlist name, and rename playlist
        dialog displays the previous name instead of "Untitled".

2003-09-02  James Willcox  <jwillcox@gnome.org>

	* lib/widgets/rb-node-view.c: (rb_node_view_set_property),
	(rb_node_view_scroll_to_node), (rb_node_view_node_is_visible):
	* lib/widgets/rb-node-view.h:

	Added rb_node_view_node_is_visible(), and use it when deciding
	whether or not to scroll when playing a node.

