2003-09-01  Yann Rouillard <yann@cvs.gnome.org>

	* shell/rb-shell.c: (rb_shell_construct):

	Moved library creation before tray icon initialization.
	This fixes segmentation fault when dnd'ing on tray icon.

2003-09-01  Metin Amiroff  <metin@karegen.com>

	* configure.ac: Added "az" in ALL_LINGUAS.

2003-09-01  desrt@desrt.ca

	* data/ui/rhythmbox-ui.xml.in:
	* shell/rb-tray-icon.c: (rb_tray_icon_init), (rb_tray_icon_new),
	(rb_tray_icon_button_press_event_cb), (sync_menu),
	(rb_tray_icon_show_window_changed_cb), (rb_tray_set_visibility):

